{"tid":972362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[放虎歸山]美國唔係1月8日前提出引渡，孟晚舟將被釋放","createTime":"2019-01-07T10:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T04:24:12.000Z","uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de3f3c5bad1e86ad1358e7d7fe6ebed700c8acc7","tid":972362,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"除鉅額保釋金外，孟晚舟更需要遵守多個條件，包括交出所有護照、住在她位於溫哥華的住所、自行聘請保安公司監控她的動向、確保通訊隨時接通、不能離開指定區域以及佩戴具有定位功能的電子定位腳鐐等。而美國政府需要於明年 1 月 8 日提出正式引渡要求，而孟晚舟則須於明年 2 月 6 日再次出席引渡聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/12/12/huawei-lawsuit/fun-tech/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2Fhuawei-lawsuit%2Ffun-tech%2F%20&d=6F2wiYdL7XsyXFQWHa%2BeTTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=20b9e7cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/12/12/huawei-lawsuit/fun-tech/ </a>"},{"pid":"1f63dd560ea723274a2f86aad311c0064d432cb7","tid":972362,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"7-8號同鄰國傾貿易戰，一傾唔掂即刻引渡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0520f6698824b6628d4119cfe4c1f1206773d7","tid":972362,"uid":202139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5a70315e873c582c4bc0ae002fab2b1bf2ffdc","tid":972362,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"Fake news?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47665dec9622287bfd9f3cbbb204ba3305468a1c","tid":972362,"uid":202139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5a70315e873c582c4bc0ae002fab2b1bf2ffdc","tid":972362,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"Fake news?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"<